---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import '../../../../styles/resources.css';
---

<Layout
  title="Blog: AI Voice Agents, Clinics & Real Estate | VivaSpeak"
  description="Practical guides on AI voice agents, call automation, clinics, real estate and HR. Learn how it works."
  canonical="https://vivaspeak.com/en/blog/"
  alternateEs="https://vivaspeak.com/blog/"
  alternateEn="https://vivaspeak.com/en/blog/"
  lang="en"
>
  <Header lang="en" />

  <main id="main-content" class="blog-container">
    <section class="resource-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="resource-title">Blog</h1>
        <p class="resource-subtitle">Guides and articles on AI voice agents and automation.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resource-grid-section">
      <div class="container resource-grid">
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>What an AI Voice Agent Is and How It Works</h3>
          <p>Complete guide on technology, call flow, latency, memory and real-world cases.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/ai-voice-agent/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>AI Voice Agent for Real Estate</h3>
          <p>How to capture more owners, filter buyers and automate property visits.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/ai-voice-real-estate/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>AI Voice Agent for Clinics</h3>
          <p>How to reduce missed calls and book more appointments with scheduling integration.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/ai-voice-clinics/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>How to Build the Perfect Knowledge Base</h3>
          <p>Recommended structure, sector examples and common mistakes to avoid.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/knowledge-base-ai-agent/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>AI Voice Agent vs Traditional IVR</h3>
          <p>Objective comparison: advantages, limitations and when to use each.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/ai-voice-agent-vs-ivr/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>AI Voice Agent vs Outsourced Call Center</h3>
          <p>Costs, quality, scalability and cases where each option makes more sense.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/ai-voice-agent-vs-call-center/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>Real Cost of Automating Calls with AI in 2026</h3>
          <p>Cost breakdown: licences, telephony, integration and comparison with alternatives.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/cost-automating-calls-ai/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-card">
          <h3>How to Choose an AI Voice Agent for Your Business</h3>
          <p>Neutral buyer guide: integrations, latency, languages, pricing and support.</p>
          <a href="/en/blog/how-to-choose-ai-voice-agent/" class="resource-link">Read article →</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" langEnHref="/en/blog/" langEsHref="/blog/" />
</Layout>
